{"tid":374670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧桂思今早病逝","createTime":"2017-08-26T02:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T02:43:41.000Z","uid":41404,"like":170,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b2c1af3873da23c42be6c7685942e72acd0582","tid":374670,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:47:38.000Z","msg":"因聯合醫院開漏藥，連累43歲鄧桂思出現肝衰竭及經歷兩次換肝手術，術後一直留醫瑪麗醫院深切治療部。消息指，鄧桂思延至今早(26日)不治離世。<br />\n<br />\n鄧桂思自今年4月起一直留醫瑪麗醫院輪候換肝，並分別於4月13日和4月20日，接受活肝及屍肝移植，惟兩次手術後均情況危殆，病情未有好轉，留醫逾4個半月，延至今日離世。"},{"pid":"91027fcf32a69243f970d64cde3396fa8c7b19ad","tid":374670,"uid":38757,"like":48,"dislike":6,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :-真係慘。。。。咁樣比醫院害死。。。。"},{"pid":"9b28b3bd325062844753deec8535e11188d55e27","tid":374670,"uid":21139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0bbc75800ac3a0d3742e1ebcbc0e53802c91c5","tid":374670,"uid":82641,"like":226,"dislike":8,"score":218,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:51:47.000Z","msg":"兩個活肝 wasted"},{"pid":"458152f11b2a979b9ef7ee56f07b02c9af151c3e","tid":374670,"uid":37487,"like":40,"dislike":8,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"口德村民全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9866b1498524f4066376edede58526766eeb37d8","tid":374670,"uid":3066,"like":80,"dislike":5,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個活肝 wasted</blockquote><br />\nD肝白捐"},{"pid":"fa2c648d633fb56db92c168f8cf37cf94fa3c38a","tid":374670,"uid":136645,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:52:53.000Z",